{"tid":1497712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大暫停駐港總領事館香港僱員往中國內地公幹 (用回鄉證, 首先是中國人)","createTime":"2019-08-23T05:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T08:04:40.000Z","uid":308875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2361309be42ef813c018a375fec6dee701571288","tid":1497712,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:47:57.000Z","msg":"加拿大傳媒報道，加拿大暫停駐港總領事館香港僱員前往中國內地公幹。(from rthk)<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一名加拿大官員透露這個消息，但他並無回應有關做法，與英國駐港總領事館香港僱員鄭文傑前往內地後，被行政拘留15日的事件是否有關。<br />\n<br />\n報道又說，加拿大全球事務部促請所有前往香港的加拿大人，對持續的示威保持高度警覺，而前往中國內地的加拿大人也要高度警覺，形容當地有隨意執法的風險。<br />\n<br />\n返大陸, 要用BC返先安全, 用回鄉證, 出左事外國政府救唔到你!<br />\n支持用BC退支籍<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 填000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1S3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=46beacae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"d14f4138e792cb140aef3faa38ee93b5043f2ee9","tid":1497712,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f55014b6d81ccff9106e891577860dd9d136d895","tid":1497712,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3c3c3baddd0b7ab56541df0499ef06b68faf9f1","tid":1497712,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1111520dffad2d70e02f20d5454e43d4ce3c1cc","tid":1497712,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84afa7ee1053799bee422a030791b5bd71e5ceaf","tid":1497712,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e222c4b3ac4dca2e4f8617918fd0307249